# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Runtime config & state (under data/)
# These carry API keys / bot identifiers / per-user workspaces — NEVER commit.
# The app auto-generates templates on first run; tracked *.example are the source.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/data/*.json
!/data/*.example
/data/farm_game.db*
/data/claude-workspace/      # Claude Bridge per-user work dirs (runtime-generated)
/data/claude-home/           # Derived by SkillInstaller from src/main/resources/skills/ — do not commit copies
/data/tasks/                 # Review video-task work dirs

